name: alloc::collections::btree::navigate::<impl collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Dying, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::LeafOrInternal>>::full_range
doc:
Splits a unique reference into a pair of leaf edges delimiting the full range of the tree.
 The results are non-unique references allowing massively destructive mutation, so must be
 used with the utmost care.
